    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A transparent yellow lake pigment used since the 16th century. It was initially extracted from unripe buckthorn berries (rhamnetin), and later from oak bark (quercitron). </Note_Text>
